672
00:41:41,830 --> 00:41:43,310
Impressive, indeed.

673
00:41:44,350 --> 00:41:45,190
Good job.

674
00:42:04,620 --> 00:42:05,500
Thank you, Miss.

675
00:42:23,470 --> 00:42:24,430
You gave all your salary

676
00:42:24,430 --> 00:42:25,470
