♪Suddenly cracked♪

700
00:43:57,920 --> 00:44:03,360
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

701
00:44:03,540 --> 00:44:07,870
♪Light encountered shadow♪

702
00:44:09,240 --> 00:44:14,630
